ygData.messageBody:
www.playerauctions.com

Most of the auctions are for pp, there are a few characters. You could
probably e-mail anyone who is selling PP and ask who on the server sells
power leveling services or characters. Level 40-55 characters are seldom
auctioned because they don't go for a lot.

- Christina
